abstract: Young trick-or-treaters showed up for the Obamas' annual White House Halloween celebration early on Saturday evening, the costumes of many of the children covered by soggy winter coats.
snippet: Young trick-or-treaters showed up for the Obamas' annual White House Halloween celebration early on Saturday evening, the costumes of many of the children covered by soggy winter coats.
lead_paragraph: If his Halloween candy didn't deter the egg throwers that President Obama feared, the weather would have.
